title: Ep. 153 - How Feminism Destroys Marriage
description:
Today we’ll talk about the poisonous effect feminism has in a marriage. Also, what are essential oils? Are they really essential? Finally, the Huffington Post has noticed some huge problems with the Rudolph the Red Nosed Reindeer story. But I’ve noticed an even bigger problem. Date: 11-30-2018
